claim.claim-text:
15. A method of affixing monofilament plastic lines together, said method comprising the steps of: 
providing a hand held device having clamping jaws and an independent source of electrical power; 
manipulating the hand held device to clamp monofilament lines together to clamp the monofilament lines between the clamping jaws in an abutting relationship in contact with each other; 
applying heat powered by the independent source of power to the monofilament lines while clamped together to melt the monofilament lines to weld the monofilament lines together.
